description: You only need two ingredients for this deliciously sweet homemade jam: blueberries and white chia seeds.
keywords: Jam,Pescatarian,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Low salt,Blueberry,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Spring,Sesame free,Quick & easy,Halal,High fibre,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Vegan,Low fat,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Two-Ingredient Blueberry Jam Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Stir blueberries in a medium saucepan over medium heat for 5 minutes, or until beginning to soften.
Using a potato masher or fork, roughly mash blueberries. Remove pan from heat and stir in chia seeds. Allow to cool and thicken for 5 minutes before storing or serving (see tip).
